videos.description: Mason Plumlee shakes his defender with a fake pass then heads to the basket to put down a two-handed dunk for the Pistons.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Plumlee breaks defender with schoolyard fake for a dunk) 2021/03/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Plumlee breaks defender with schoolyard fake for a dunk

videos.description: Saben Lee throws an alley-oop inbound pass to Isaiah Stewart who throws down an emphatic slam for the Pistons.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Stewart slams down alley-oop off inbound pass) 2021/03/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stewart slams down alley-oop off inbound pass

videos.description: Isaiah Stewart is assessed a flagrant 2 foul and is ejected from the game, while Blake Griffin is assessed a technical foul for flopping.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Stewart gets tossed after throwing elbow at Blake Griffin) 2021/03/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stewart gets tossed after throwing elbow at Blake Griffin

videos.description: While falling to the ground, Mason Plumlee throws a no-look bounce pass over his head to Saddiq Bey for a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Plumlee throws no-look bounce pass while falling for assist) 2021/03/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Plumlee throws no-look bounce pass while falling for assist

videos.description: James Harden throws a lob to DeAndre Jordan who goes up to flush a reverse dunk for the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden finds Jordan for reverse alley-oop dunk) 2021/03/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden finds Jordan for reverse alley-oop dunk

videos.description: DeAndre Jordan drives from outside the 3-point line and takes flight to smash down an authoritative one-handed slam for the Nets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Jordan skies to throw down ferocious dunk) 2021/03/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan skies to throw down ferocious dunk

videos.description: Blake Griffin stares down the Pistons bench and yells out some heated comments after he throws down an alley-oop jam off the pass from James Harden.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Griffin stares down Pistons bench after big dunk on Harden feed) 2021/03/26 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin stares down Pistons bench after big dunk on Harden feed

videos.description: James Harden scores 44 points tying his season high and setting a Nets' season high as Brooklyn goes on to defeat the Pistons 113-111.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Harden sets his Nets' high with 44 points) 2021/03/26 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Harden sets his Nets' high with 44 points

videos.description: Blake Griffin struggles to find the camera in a postgame interview after the Nets defeat the Pistons in a thriller.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Griffin struggles to find camera in postgame interview) 2021/03/26 ESHEET
